      "code_hash": "a91472f39c9641966d6068dc25ce1de4",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"siege-of-winterfell-7th-anniversary-strategy-optimizer\">Siege of Winterfell \u2014 7th Anniversary Strategy Optimizer</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">This notebook models the <strong>Siege of Winterfell (7th Anniversary Special Edition)</strong> event.\nIt simulates a 60-minute battle and grid-searches over deployment allocations to find\nthe strategy that maximises total alliance points.</span>\n<h2 id=\"scoring-channels\">Scoring channels</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>First capture</strong> \u2014 one-time points when your alliance first occupies a building.</li>\n<li><strong>Occupation</strong> \u2014 points per minute for each building you control.</li>\n<li><strong>Treasure digging</strong> \u2014 treasures spawn at random locations from minute 8. Normal = 80 pts, Rare = 120 pts.</li>\n<li><strong>Dragon escort</strong> \u2014 Twin dragons spawn at minute 12. Each worth 3,000 pts. Majority controls escort direction.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"map-timeline\">Map timeline</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Period</th>\n<th>Minutes</th>\n<th>Events</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>0\u20138</td>\n<td>Outposts, Armory, Hot Spring available</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>8\u201312</td>\n<td>Treasure spawning begins</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>12\u201360</td>\n<td>Strongholds unlock, Dragons spawn</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
